Show Description

From the Infowars web site :: On this guest-packed Wednesday, June 19 edition of The Alex Jones Show, former Congressman Ron Paul joins us to discuss the impending dollar collapse, the NSA's constitutional infringements and other privacy scandals. 

Alex also speaks with comedian and prankster Tom Mabe who recently filmed a powerful satire video portraying himself as a NSA agent "recording" people in public with a boom mike.

In studio, Alex hosts cancer survivor Genae Girard, who recently won a Supreme Court case against patents on naturally occurring DNA. The victory has already lowered the cost of breast cancer testing.
